<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 pàn wàng hǎo xiāo xī, cóng nà chuāng wài lái,
 pàn wàng hǎo xiāo xī, cóng nà yuǎn fāng lái;
 zài yáng guāng yǔ lù zhōng zài fēng shōu jì jié lǐ
 zài qiū fēng qiū yǔ lǐ yǒu wǒ zhī dào de hǎo xiāo xī.
 nà jiù shì píng ān, guī yú ài shén de rén.
 nà jiù shì zhù fú, cháng bàn suí tā men,
 yuàn tā men hēng tōng jiǎo tà zhī de liú zhī yóu
 guǒ shí lèi lèi, fú bēi mǎn yì.</lyrics>
<title>pàn wàng hǎo xiāo xī 迦南60</title>
<hymn_number>60</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>